cs.NI, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.CR

This paper discusses the application of self-organized network management and machine learning in the context of cellular networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses the challenges associated with network management, which could place it in cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
